{"tid":1787071,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"耶耶托尼：奧斯爾不應批評內地人權","createTime":"2019-12-17T15:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T12:17:55.000Z","uid":79562,"like":3,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9351b9a03a6a11ac66081b22ed460220974e7b87","tid":1787071,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>耶耶托尼：奧斯爾不應批評內地人權</strong><br />\n\r<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_369&amp;itemid=1239570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_369%26itemid%3D1239570&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BuuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b7ab4290\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_369&amp;itemid=1239570</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n曾效力巴塞羅那及曼城的科特迪瓦中場耶耶托尼，評論阿仙奴中場奧斯爾批評中國打壓新疆維吾爾族人的貼文，認為對方不應該發表有關言論。耶耶托尼說，作為足球員應該留在足球世界，因為伊斯蘭教是一個複雜的議題，牽涉其中會引來很多問題。現時效力青島黃海的耶耶托尼說，自己很喜歡足球，一直堅守不牽涉政治的宗旨。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n土耳其裔的奧斯爾上星期在社交網貼出詩句，指摘西方穆斯林社會對中國迫害新疆維吾爾人，視以不見，更貼上「東突厥斯坦」的旗幟，受到內地網民批評及媒體杯葛。"},{"pid":"f61bae0cd97b23e7101757f0a8d3a1d4840082ba","tid":1787071,"uid":25506,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"耶耶托柒"},{"pid":"1b13d103dcace0d41b5b65592737c811f5b7ee52","tid":1787071,"uid":5378,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"民主自由 死黑鬼點會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb3976fbdd7ad298871d83d428d7162dc614325","tid":1787071,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b13d103dcace0d41b5b65592737c811f5b7ee52","tid":1787071,"uid":5378,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"民主自由 死黑鬼點會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"